text: Andreu Canals Butcher (born 10 February 1973) is a Spanish rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Toledo, Spain
